                    <note type="abstract" xml:id="abstract-en-1126">In hagiography: Amai was a Persian Martyr
          from the region of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/993">Adiabene</placeName>. She
          was a daughter of the covenant who was killed with other daughters of the covenant,
          including Thecla.</note>
